  "detailed_description": "<h1>Supports Valve Index (and Index Controllers)</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/61130e100b738a881608dc0f5adc710f.poster.avif?t=1743532611\" width=640 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/61130e100b738a881608dc0f5adc710f.webm?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/61130e100b738a881608dc0f5adc710f.mp4?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Fujii</i> fully supports the Valve Index HMD and the Valve Index Controllers.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/8baf7a1875be45b0e9085995d61eb1b7.poster.avif?t=1743532611\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/8baf7a1875be45b0e9085995d61eb1b7.webm?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/8baf7a1875be45b0e9085995d61eb1b7.mp4?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Fujii</i> is a meditative and magical journey through dreamlike landscapes filled with light and wonder. <br><br>An adorable gnome companion welcomes you home. It’s the beautiful garden of your dreams, ready to come to life through the mystical power that lies at your fingertips. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/76fd88d8da0c3a4cea36fa2679565285.poster.avif?t=1743532611\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/76fd88d8da0c3a4cea36fa2679565285.webm?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/76fd88d8da0c3a4cea36fa2679565285.mp4?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rejuvenate your soul as you affectionately nurture bountiful seeds, solve gentle puzzles, and explore otherworldly biomes eager to surprise and delight you. Take a breath, allow yourself to forget the troubles of the real world, and bask in this serene and uplifting experience about caring and cultivating.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌿 <u>FEATURES</u> 🌿</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore three organic biomes filled with magic, enchanted flowers, and beautiful plants<br></li><li>Nurture your own unique garden by collecting seeds to harvest colorful landscapes<br></li><li>Introduce gentle critters to your garden and solve puzzles with your adorable gnome companion by your side<br></li><li>Embark on a peaceful and whimsical adventure set to a meditative soundscape composed by French artist and composer Norman Bambi</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/3402be38f4554e0f6ded41907b984e72.poster.avif?t=1743532611\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/3402be38f4554e0f6ded41907b984e72.webm?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/3402be38f4554e0f6ded41907b984e72.mp4?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/8baf7a1875be45b0e9085995d61eb1b7.poster.avif?t=1743532611\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/8baf7a1875be45b0e9085995d61eb1b7.webm?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/8baf7a1875be45b0e9085995d61eb1b7.mp4?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Fujii</i> is a meditative and magical journey through dreamlike landscapes filled with light and wonder. <br><br>An adorable gnome companion welcomes you home. It’s the beautiful garden of your dreams, ready to come to life through the mystical power that lies at your fingertips. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/76fd88d8da0c3a4cea36fa2679565285.poster.avif?t=1743532611\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/76fd88d8da0c3a4cea36fa2679565285.webm?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/76fd88d8da0c3a4cea36fa2679565285.mp4?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rejuvenate your soul as you affectionately nurture bountiful seeds, solve gentle puzzles, and explore otherworldly biomes eager to surprise and delight you. Take a breath, allow yourself to forget the troubles of the real world, and bask in this serene and uplifting experience about caring and cultivating.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌿 <u>FEATURES</u> 🌿</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore three organic biomes filled with magic, enchanted flowers, and beautiful plants<br></li><li>Nurture your own unique garden by collecting seeds to harvest colorful landscapes<br></li><li>Introduce gentle critters to your garden and solve puzzles with your adorable gnome companion by your side<br></li><li>Embark on a peaceful and whimsical adventure set to a meditative soundscape composed by French artist and composer Norman Bambi</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/3402be38f4554e0f6ded41907b984e72.poster.avif?t=1743532611\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/3402be38f4554e0f6ded41907b984e72.webm?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/589040/extras/3402be38f4554e0f6ded41907b984e72.mp4?t=1743532611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
